title: 820-00165 Missing PP5v_S4RS3
message:
Macbook Air 820-00165

History:
problem with PP3v42 and water damage.


I fixed the problem and put the board into ultrasonic cleaning and after the ultrasonic cleaning, the board doesn't work.

I have:
PP3v42 = 3.42v
PP5v_s5 = 5v
PP3v3_s5 = 3.3v
PPVRTC = 3.3v


PP5v_S4RS3 = Missing!!! 0v

Checking PM_slp_s4 now.. But cant find anything? Yet!

title: 820-00165 Missing PP5v_S4RS3
message:
Did you use sweep function of UC machine?

Check the board for knocked off components and broken traces.
UC machine just removes corrosion, doesn't rebuild corroded traces.

title: 820-00165 Missing PP5v_S4RS3
message: UC it again and dry it properly...

title: 820-00165 Missing PP5v_S4RS3
message: Use distilled water adding proper cleaning liquid, no IPA.

title: 820-00165 Missing PP5v_S4RS3
message: Yes as 2informaticos said distilled only and cleaning solution recommend Branson EC

title: 820-00165 Missing PP5v_S4RS3
message:
Problem is solved gents.. Someone mentioned issued with pm_slp_s4. so I started there and traced back. 

Was missing pm_slp_s5 rail as well. So i continue tracing back

It was U8020 (TPS22924) Missing 3v output voltage. It had pp3v3_s5 input and pp3v3_sus_en input.
